    • Field Detail

      • id

        private int id
        The ID is used to identify a specific bike. The ID is unique within a bike type (electric/normal).

      • model

        protected java.lang.String model
        Identifying model name for the respective bike. Protected is visible within a package and all subclasses.

      • color

        protected java.lang.String color
        Color of the respective bike. This variable - and others in this class - are protected (and not private) because they are used in the to String of the sub-class ElectricBikes. Protected variables are accessible within all classes in the same package and within subclasses in other packages.

      • bikeType

        protected java.lang.String bikeType
        bikeType is either: men, women, unisex.

      • price

        protected int price
        The Price is provided as price/day in DKK.

      • isAvailable

        private boolean isAvailable
        boolean isAvailable indicates if the bike can be rented out or not (e.g. true = yes, bike is available).

        newColor - -- Color of bike
